description: Use Bun for all JavaScript package and script workflows
alwaysApply: true
---

# Bun Only

- Use `bun install`, `bun run`, and `bun test` for JavaScript and TypeScript work in this repo.
- Do not use `npm`, `npx`, `pnpm`, or `yarn`.
- Do not create or update `package-lock.json`, `pnpm-lock.yaml`, or `yarn.lock`.
- Prefer `bun add` and `bun add -d` when adding JavaScript dependencies.
- If a command example uses npm syntax, translate it to the Bun equivalent before running it.
